Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,LEFT CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,KISUKE URAHARA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,BIRTHDAY,0000,0000,0000,,12/31
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,RIGHT CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,YORUICHI SHIHOIN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,BIRTHDAY,0000,0000,0000,,1/1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.91,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud.\NThat Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:44.31,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Ditching her duties...\NWhere'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.55,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.44,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, she is such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.54,B2,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy New Year's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.50,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:56.03,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.34,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:05.64,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now begin the Women's Soul Reaper\NAssociation New Year's party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.64,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with our Chairwoman passing\Nout monetary gifts for the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.69,B2,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.53,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Such a cute envelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:19.40,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,It is cute, but... A giraffe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:21.93,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,A cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.08,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:25.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:29.54,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Your envelope has a bear,\NCaptain Soi Fon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.33,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.59,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,And I will also pass out my Squad's\NNew Year's cards, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:38.26,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Chairwoman, aren't New Year's\Ncards ordinarily mailed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.72,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,HAPPY NEW YEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.56,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,How silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.06,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:47.18,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.96,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.57,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:56.76,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I realize it's New Year's, but you mustn't\Nneglect your Soul Reaper duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.18,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.18,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.65,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these New\NYear's cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.02,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,They're disgraceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.03,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Please collect all of these unbeautiful\NNew Year's cards
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.37,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,and make ones that\Nare more decent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:10.58,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.50,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,More decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.79,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HAPPY NEW YEAR\NFROM SQUAD 10
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.30,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.22,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.66,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Matsumoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:23.82,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.93,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I believe New Year's card designs are the\Nprerogative of the person who sends them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.77,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.04,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.48,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Squad 7 is using Captain\NKomamura's photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:40.74,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WISHING YOU A\NHAPPY NEW YEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.13,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not even the\Nyear of the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.84,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,He has nothing to do with\Nthe Chinese Zodiac!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.74,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.45,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HAPPY NEW YEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.00,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the year of the cat this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.45,B2,HITSUGAYA'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.92,B2,SOI FON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...Lady Yoruichi's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.01,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.98,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,There's a New Year's card\Nfor you as well, Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:57.67,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.31,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:01.72,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.22,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to send one to Soi Fon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.56,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,My preference would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.01,B2,HITSUGAYA'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,That's no longer a\NNew Year's card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:15.10,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,I'd preferred it if I were\Na bit shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.02,B2,HITSUGAYA'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you about\Nyour height complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.29,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:24.80,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Why do women keep changing the\Nsubject, Captain Hitsugaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.42,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.85,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,There's way too much mixing\Nof work and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.20,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Captain Hitsugaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.46,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Will you quit asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.03,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I like what\Nyou just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.50,B2,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.18,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Comments that look\Ndown upon women
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.65,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,are absolutely unacceptable,\NCaptain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.51,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:47.88,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, isn't it petty for men to\Nbe making all sorts of comments
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.95,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,over a small thing like\NNew Year's cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.22,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.84,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go there, Ikkaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.89,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win an argument\Nagainst women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.39,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.43,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying we women\Nare nothing but talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:03.16,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.54,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:08.17,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,We won't lose to men,\Nand not just at arguments!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.99,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose we'll have to\Nsettle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.03,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi! Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.42,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,As a man, I have my share\Nof pride to uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.42,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:20.97,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.38,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:25.89,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.34,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.56,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this,\Nit'll be the women versus the men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.27,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,in a fight to the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:43.87,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,The First Annual,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.45,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Men vs Women: New Year's\NWhacky Karuta Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:50.41,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Why karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.33,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.23,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Aren't you going to explain\Nthe rules, Chairwoman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:59.88,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You know the rules. It's\Na regular karuta game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.88,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the first card is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:07.07,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's early morning; \NThe Third Seat Madarame. \NThe year's first sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.76,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,It's early morning;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.22,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Seat Madarame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.09,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,The year's first sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.05,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.24,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The New Year has come; \NThe Third Seat Madarame. \NLarge stacked rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.08,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,The New Year has come;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.24,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Seat Madarame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.26,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Large stacked rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.21,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:21.50,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He hit the jackpot; \N The Third Seat Madarame. \N Pachinko ball face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.91,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,He hit the jackpot;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.12,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Seat Madarame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.52,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Pachinko ball face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.75,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.89,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.17,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling you're\Npicking on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:31.51,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,That third card... What's\Nwith the pachinko balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.86,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do\Nwith New Year's!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.12,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,You are ejected for arguing\Nwith a game judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.91,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.99,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of rule is that?!\NI never heard of that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.50,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,I never mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.05,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,THIRD SEAT MADARAME\NEJECTED FROM GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:50.99,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Year of the Rabbit \NOf course, even doggies, too,  \Nwear rabbit ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.27,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Year of the Rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.64,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, even doggies, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.01,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,wear rabbit ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.14,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.43,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.35,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.77,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.88,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.99,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,She has a further\Nreach than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.78,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:16.85,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Greeting the New Year \Nsaying prayers of long life  \Nfor the Head Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.71,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Greeting the New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.13,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,saying prayers of long life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.87,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,for the Head Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.99,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,It starts with "Greeting\Nthe New Year," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:24.88,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Gre...gre...gre...gre...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.26,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.01,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Gre...gre...gre...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.55,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gre...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:34.51,B2,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.51,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,LIEUTENANT HISAGI TEMPORARILY\NEXITS DUE TO INJURIES
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.74,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Outrageous... So outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.81,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.06,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Using your "weapons"\Nto make Hisagi bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.80,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You would go that far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.74,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,He started bleeding from\Nthe nose on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:57.14,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Festive New Year's broth \N with freshly pounded rice cakes \NGegetsuburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.99,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Festive New Year's broth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.45,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,with freshly pounded rice cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.16,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Gegetsuburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.26,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.00,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head, Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.58,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.95,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.79,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,That's going way too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.42,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Judge! Wasn't that illegal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.47,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.37,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Zabimaru... \N Was that the year of the monkey, \N or the year of the snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.18,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.35,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the year of the monkey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.39,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,or the year of the snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.02,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't even listening to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.81,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,And that wasn't even\Nin 5-7-5 form!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.88,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Za...za...za...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.05,B2,NEMU,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:43.85,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Worthy of display\N Beautiful and radiant\N You and New Year's day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.43,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Worthy of display
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.80,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful and radiant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.87,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,You and New Year's day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.13,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number 4: Hainawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.26,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.63,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 31:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.38,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Shakkaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.89,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, back to the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.61,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.23,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,We're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:13.64,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Why...is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.41,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,LIEUTENANT HISAGI EXITS ONCE\NAGAIN DUE TO INJURIES
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.14,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,Putting up a kite
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:24.39,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Putting up a kite\N is so much easier with\N a good pair of shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.83,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,is so much easier with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.41,B2,YACHIRU'S VOICE,0000,0000,0000,,a good pair of shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.08,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.46,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number 30:\NShitotsusansen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.78,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:35.75,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.56,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.18,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.98,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,So that one was a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.78,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.14,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.94,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hado Number 58: Tenran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.29,B2,NANAO,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number 62:\NHyapporankan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.52,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom! Fujikujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.56,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.96,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Yoruichi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.09,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Not among the Zodiac
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.70,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Consolation prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:27.12,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,That card...is Lady Yoruichi's.\NThat card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.77,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.61,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.46,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.56,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.73,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, was there something\Nyou wanted to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.06,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:18.79,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.22,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.88,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I will try to do my best this\Nyear in good spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.60,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,The first-of-the-New-Year shrine visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.68,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how everyone's spending\Ntheir New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like the store is going anywhere,\Nand nor is your New Year's monetary gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So slow down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.79,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.57,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making\Nme carry all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.80,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:50.15,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even carry one\Nor two game consoles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:54.04,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save my energy to\Nplay them when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:57.22,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious you're planning to play\Nthese the moment you get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:57.71,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.92,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to monopolize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.44,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.04,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No fair! You always\Nget to play first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:01.93,B2,MIZUHO,0000,0000,0000,,Quit whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.51,B2,KEIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:18.28,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's how Ishida spends\Ntime with family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:23.11,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone spends New Year's\Nwith their families, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.78,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's so nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.99,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure it must be the same\Nat Tatsuki's place too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.23,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wouldn't be right for\Nme to bother them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.35,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,Why am I being so gloomy at\Nthe start of the New Year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.76,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,Happy! Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.46,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,I've got to be cheery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.01,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Why the huge yawn so\Nearly in the New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.47,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:56.57,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Iba and the others made me\Nparty with them deep into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and the others would laugh\Nif they could see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.59,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.42,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and finish our rounds\Nof New Year's greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.28,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry home\Nand go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.49,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:13.66,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kuchiki and...Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.31,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.98,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.33,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.57,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.74,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about making the\Nfirst-of-the-New-Year shrine visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.72,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:32.38,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But it looked crowded, so I\Nfigured it didn't have to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.89,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Are the two of you on your\Nway to a shrine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:38.00,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No, we came to the World\Nof the Living as part of our
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.35,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,rounds of New Year's greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.91,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.26,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be meeting with\Na lot of people today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.60,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,So you've already met\Nwith some people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:52.56,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was Kurosaki, Ishida,\Nand my school friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.08,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't say "met,"\Nsince I only saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.79,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,So Ichigo and the others\Nare nearby? Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.07,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get our New Year's greetings\Nover with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.83,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.53,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.69,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is spending today\Nwith their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.43,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'd be right to interrupt\Ntheir family time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what New Year's is like\Nin the World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:21.10,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,There are people like me too,\Nso I think there are all kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.16,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.45,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's go\Nsomewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.47,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You come with us too, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.24,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.45,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:39.37,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.98,B2,URAHARA SHOP MEMBERS,0000,0000,0000,,Yoisho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.21,B2,URAHARA SHOP MEMBERS,0000,0000,0000,,Yoisho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.34,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known\Nwe'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.80,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, you three.\NHappy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.23,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.66,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,We're pounding rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:01.92,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted to do something festive\Nfor New Year's, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.40,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.38,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.40,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.86,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.03,B2,JINTA,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:16.99,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Yoisho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.75,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Almost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.89,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "almost"?!\NSounds like you want me to get hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.69,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to\Naim for the mortar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.26,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.55,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.55,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Yoisho!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:36.87,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.52,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.21,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Silly! Why're you hitting\Nit back nice and easy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.48,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.77,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,You suck, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:02.70,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I haven't had\Nenough sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.24,B2,URURU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.96,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait... You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:13.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, aren't you wearing\Ntoo much ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.62,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty inked up\Nyourself, Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.39,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.81,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,We're nothing compared to Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.85,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.74,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Nuts and Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.14,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:32.32,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes are all stained,\Nso why don't you change into these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.64,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.81,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Kimonos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:40.59,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I feel I've totally experienced\NNew Year's now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:43.17,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Now all that's left is the\Nfirst-of-the-New-Year shrine visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.43,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine visit, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.92,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go on the\Nway home then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.04,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,No way, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.00,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.59,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.68,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Now see here, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:00.60,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Sea bream holds a special place\Nin the New Year's feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.87,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, they talked of "staring\Nat the sea bream,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.06,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,where no one touched the sea bream for\Nthe first three days of the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.12,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,There is literature that\Ndescribes how,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:10.67,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,even today, the custom of not eating sea\Nbream on New Year's day still remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.23,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.53,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.82,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:21.95,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you hit me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.16,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Kid! Watch\Nwhere you hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:29.54,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that really sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.34,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew this was\Ngoing to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.68,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have come to make\Nmy New Year's rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.42,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.13,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.59,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't enjoyed New Year's\Nthis much in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.58,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you had a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:46.48,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,But why do I always get stuck\Nwith the short end of the stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:51.56,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's is meant to be a\Ntime when you mellow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.39,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.44,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,but whether you're feeling mellow or not,\Nit's not fun if you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.12,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.13,B2,TESSAI,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's broth is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.54,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,The New Year's broth, he said.\NLet's have some, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:17.36,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You too, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.84,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.10,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see you, Inoue, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.35,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Get home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.73,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You can return the\Nkimono next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.66,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.29,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.92,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.76,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:52.84,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:53.88,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.80,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we making a\NNew Year's shrine visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.25,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's gotten pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:06.67,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,The people are probably gone,\Nso I don't think it'll be all that much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.67,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:13.81,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But the vendors are probably gone,\Nand we can't pull our fortune predictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.46,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Let's go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.86,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.06,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:29.35,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,But we came all this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.28,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,so let's say our prayers\Nbefore we go back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.68,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,even though we'll\Nbe by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then include us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.27,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:57.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.69,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.19,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stranger, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.82,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You could've at least called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.25,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.03,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Sado...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.60,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.54,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.04,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.26,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting off the\NNew Year like a taskmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.45,0:21:21.48,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.60,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:26.67,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with.\NI want to go back and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:28.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You just won't admit it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.28,B2,RENJI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.79,B2,ORIHIME (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I pray for another enjoyable year\Ntogether with everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:21.19,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:23.67,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What, Rukia? You're small!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you again, Rukiruki.\NThen this must be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:28.63,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a dream!\NAnd I'm not Rukiruki either!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Don't poke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:30.63,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:31.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:31.89,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:33.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:34.56,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:36.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:40.34,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,This sure was an eventful year,\Nwasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:41.76,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:44.27,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall we put\Non the finishing touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:48.36,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday, Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:50.32,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday, Kisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.95,0:24:02.32,B2,URAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,No one remembered\Nagain this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:04.31,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of sad, isn't it?